name: The Rosemary Dress
description:
Looking like a piece straight out of Grandmas glory box. The Rosemary dress is covered in a boquet of flowers in natural earthy tones with hints of rose pink. The Rosemary dress buttons down to the waist, also has shoulder pads and a sophisticated collar neckline. Elastic waist has some stretch and comes with matching belt. Works just as well for summer tea parties as it does with boots and tights in winter. ( Great layering piece )
